data.description: Located 5 minutes from University of West Georgia campus  and 3 minutes to the greenbelt trailhead, this property is ideal for student housing.  With hardwood flooring, new roof, new HVAC, spend time enjoying the oversized deck, spacious level back yard, covered parking, mature trees, convenient to all that Carrollton City living has to offer.  3D digital twin under virtual tour tab.
